        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Investing for Tomorrow's Schools Act </b></p> <p>This bill provides for the establishment&nbsp;of state infrastructure banks for the purpose of funding education infrastructure projects. The bill sets forth requirements for the banks, including requirements related to funding, qualifying projects, building standards, and loan terms. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
